{"tid":1641363,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新港城7pm閂門","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:39:24.000Z","uid":302130,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"10df8df960abf03a759984f284ad42d21a5219e8","tid":1641363,"uid":302130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:14:04.000Z","msg":"From MOSTown Management:<br />\n<br />\nWe are aware of potential large-scale public event on MOSTown. For the safety of tenants and customers, MOSTown is closed on 19:00, 9 October. If any assistance is needed, please contact our staff at 2631 0334. We apologize for any inconvenience caused.<br />\n<br />\n新港城中心商場管理處示<br />\n留意到新港城中心可能會出現大型公眾活動，為顧及商戶及顧客的安全，新港城中心商場於10月9日7時正暫停營業。各商戶如需協助，請致電2631 0334與管理處職員聯絡。不便之處，敬請原諒。<br />\n<br />\n1810 現場已經有記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ffa6b6df2447492177e9505be2b4e27fcd69c2","tid":1641363,"uid":302130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"幫推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f3fb4211805979981c7c1ac52be05140693202","tid":1641363,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:15:11.000Z","msg":"咁仲去唔去 ?"},{"pid":"33716f151d2fc0a7b41fd80eba06d077a38753ba","tid":1641363,"uid":302130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:15:17.000Z","msg":"光復新港城<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165cb8dfd42f55a1e0f85e00987b45399e463adf","tid":1641363,"uid":302130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:16:08.000Z","msg":"早啲入黎行街呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752b0f948c14d6b76336e55e526d6ce638f205cc","tid":1641363,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4f3fb4211805979981c7c1ac52be05140693202","tid":1641363,"uid":254